Package guru.mikelue.jdut.decorate

Interface DataGrainDecorator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TableSchemaLoadingDecorator
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
    @FunctionalInterface
public interface DataGrainDecorator
    This interface should be used with DataGrain.decorate(guru.mikelue.jdut.decorate.DataGrainDecorator).

    Chaining

    You could chaining a bunch of decorators: 
    
 // decorator - The first decorator
 // nextDecorator - The next decorator
 decorator = decorator.chain(nextDecorator);
